        <div id="left_column">
            <h2>About Me</h2>

<p>I'm an applied mathematician with broad interests. I like structures, spaces, dynamics.</p>

<p>View <a href="http://ltwp.net/projects/writing">my writing</a> and <a href="http://ltwp.net/projects/workshops">my workshops</a>.</p>

<p>I am currently finishing my time as an undergraduate at Brown University. I am a TA in the Division of Applied Mathematics and am the head manager at the <a href="http://www.brown.edu/research/projects/design-workshop/about-us">Brown Design Workshop</a>, where I was a founding member. I give tours at the <a href="http://risdmuseum.org">RISD Museum</a>.</p>

<p>Previously, professionally, I have done fluids research on an NSF grant, technical research on social systems and networks at <a href="http://thisisthicket.net">Thicket</a>, and furniture building with <a href="http://borisbally.com">Boris Bally</a>. I continue to be associated with <a href="http://brown.steamwith.us">Brown STEAM</a>.</p>

<p>Some skills I can offer:</p>

<ul>
<li>Interdisciplinary Research</li>
<li>Dynamic and agent-based modeling</li>
<li>MATLAB, Mathematica, LaTeX</li>
<li>Workshop Planning and Execution</li>
<li>Microsoft and Google document suites</li>
<li>Wood- and Metal-working</li>
<li>Adobe Photoshop and Illustrator</li>
<li>Fabric Construction</li>
<li>HTML/CSS</li>
<li>Javascript, jQuery, various libraries.</li>
<li>Arduino &amp; Processing</li>
<li>Rhino 3D (currently learning)</li>
<li>Python (currently learning)</li>
</ul>

<p>Elsewhere: <a href="http://www.last.fm/user/ltwp">last.fm</a> / <a href="https://github.com/ltwp">github</a> / <a href="http://www.ltwp.yelp.com">yelp</a> / <a href="https://pinboard.in/u:lukas">pinboard</a> / <a href="https://www.are.na/lukas-wp">are.na</a></p>


